  <Properties>
    <contentGrid>
      <Value><![CDATA[{
  "contentData": [
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "f170b29c-338f-4ab8-a5c4-f72c90826f69",
      "key": "4cd55aeb-7202-4636-b8ad-9eb5285df696",
      "values": []
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "c345e5ce-768f-47e0-968a-e7859dbe0b07",
      "key": "426a4cc3-8b98-41bf-92eb-5e3ad7a1f4a9",
      "values": []
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "d5bfea49-0733-48ff-9ee0-d83c01a4cbf4",
      "key": "d23e4db8-daeb-4b0f-92c2-a26af32e5b1e",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "What It Does"
        },
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureDescription",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Displays child pages of the current page as a responsive card grid"
        },
        {
          "alias": "richTextContent",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "Layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EThe Internal Links - Children feature automatically lists all child pages of the current page as a responsive grid of Bootstrap cards. Each card shows the child page\u0027s thumbnail, title, and description with a stretched link that makes the entire card clickable.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis feature is ideal for section landing pages where you want to present the available sub-pages visually. It requires no configuration \u2014 it discovers child pages automatically from the content tree and renders them using the page\u0027s own properties.\u003C/p\u003E"
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureSummary",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "The card grid is responsive: 1 column on mobile, 2 at md, 3 at lg."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "d5bfea49-0733-48ff-9ee0-d83c01a4cbf4",
      "key": "1f3793df-c85b-4b8c-b360-9685335098e5",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "How It Works"
        },
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureDescription",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Reads child pages from the content tree and renders them as cards with thumbnails"
        },
        {
          "alias": "richTextContent",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "Layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EThe view accesses child pages through \u003Ccode\u003EUmbracoContext.PublishedRequest.PublishedContent.Children\u0026lt;WebPage\u0026gt;()\u003C/code\u003E, which returns strongly-typed child pages. Each child\u0027s \u003Ccode\u003EPageTitle\u003C/code\u003E, \u003Ccode\u003EPageDescription\u003C/code\u003E, and \u003Ccode\u003EPageThumbnail\u003C/code\u003E properties are used to populate the card.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESVG thumbnails receive special treatment \u2014 instead of rendering as an \u003Ccode\u003E\u0026lt;img\u0026gt;\u003C/code\u003E tag, the SVG file is read from disk and inlined directly into the HTML. This enables dark mode support, since inline SVGs inherit CSS colour properties while \u003Ccode\u003E\u0026lt;img\u0026gt;\u003C/code\u003E tags do not.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENon-SVG images use Umbraco\u0027s \u003Ccode\u003EGetCropUrl()\u003C/code\u003E to generate optimised thumbnails at 480px width.\u003C/p\u003E"
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureSummary",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Cards use Bootstrap\u0027s shadow and stretched-link utilities for hover effects and full-card clickability."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "f444fff5-9769-4376-a831-f3c6ac6cba0f",
      "key": "5bc201c6-afaf-440b-b09a-94c9e5b0b3b9",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Example: Child Pages"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "c4b3a613-0d2c-4470-8d06-f7efea52d6e0",
